statements.sql: select `scale`.`name` as `scale_name`, `minrals`.`minral_name` as `mineral_name`, `provinces`.`name` as `province`, `provinces`.`province_code` as `province_id`, COUNT(weight.id) as cars, SUM(mineral_net_weight) AS total_mineral_weight, SUM(CASE WHEN discharge_place = 'CHECKED' THEN 200 ELSE mineral_net_weight * 10 END) as total_revenue from `scale_system`.`weight` inner join `scale` on `weight`.`scale_id` = `scale`.`id` inner join `provinces` on `scale`.`department_id` = `provinces`.`province_code` inner join `minrals` on `minrals`.`id` = `weight`.`mineral_id` group by `scale`.`id`, `minrals`.`id`, `provinces`.`name` order by `scale_name` asc

select `scale`.`name`, SUM(CASE WHEN discharge_place = "CHECKED" THEN 200 ELSE mineral_net_weight * 10 END) AS Total_Revenue from `weight` inner join `scale` on `weight`.`scale_id` = `scale`.`id` group by `scale`.`name`

select SUM(CASE WHEN discharge_place = 'CHECKED' THEN 200 ELSE mineral_net_weight * 10 END) as total_revenue from `weight` where `weight`.`created_at` between '2024-09-22' and '2024-10-21' group by `weight`.`mineral_id`, `weight`.`discharge_place`

select `scale`.`name`, `weight`.`mineral_id`, COUNT(weight.id) as cars, SUM(weight.mineral_net_weight) AS Total_Mineral_Weight, SUM(CASE WHEN discharge_place = 'CHECKED' THEN 200 ELSE mineral_net_weight * 10 END) as total_revenue, `weight`.`discharge_place`, `weight`.`discharge_place` from `weight` left join `scale` on `weight`.`scale_id` = `scale`.`id` where `weight`.`created_at` between '2024-10-22' and '2024-11-20' group by `scale`.`name`, `weight`.`mineral_id`, `weight`.`discharge_place`

select `scale`.`name`, `weight`.`mineral_id`, COUNT(weight.id) as cars, SUM(weight.mineral_net_weight) AS Total_Mineral_Weight, SUM(CASE WHEN discharge_place = 'CHECKED' THEN 200 ELSE mineral_net_weight * 10 END) as total_revenue, `weight`.`discharge_place` from `weight` left join `scale` on `weight`.`scale_id` = `scale`.`id` where `weight`.`created_at` between '2024-03-20' and '2025-03-21' and year(`weight`.`created_at`) = '2024' group by `scale`.`name`, `weight`.`mineral_id`, `weight`.`discharge_place`
